org.apache.hadoop.hbase.replication

类 ReplicationPeers

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hbase.replication.ReplicationPeers

  • @InterfaceAudience.Private
public class ReplicationPeers
extends Object
    This provides an class for maintaining a set of peer clusters. These peers are remote slave clusters that data is replicated to.

      • addPeer

        public boolean addPeer(String peerId)
                throws ReplicationException
        Method called after a peer has been connected. It will create a ReplicationPeer to track the newly connected cluster.
        参数:
        peerId - a short that identifies the cluster
        返回:
        whether a ReplicationPeer was successfully created
        抛出:
        ReplicationException

      • removePeer

        public void removePeer(String peerId)

      • getPeer

        public ReplicationPeerImpl getPeer(String peerId)
        Returns the ReplicationPeerImpl for the specified cached peer. This ReplicationPeer will continue to track changes to the Peer's state and config. This method returns null if no peer has been cached with the given peerId.
        参数:
        peerId - id for the peer
        返回:
        ReplicationPeer object

      • getAllPeerIds

        public Set<String> getAllPeerIds()
        Returns the set of peerIds of the clusters that have been connected and have an underlying ReplicationPeer.
        返回:
        a Set of Strings for peerIds
